body.description: Here’s something to harp on—Angel Soft Mega Rolls last and last with rolls that are 4 times as big as our Regular Rolls. With 320 2-ply sheets on every Mega Roll, you’ll always have plenty of the softness and strength you love on hand. Plus, each generously sized roll still fits harmoniously in most standard bathroom toilet paper holders. And like all your favorite Angel Soft products, our Mega Rolls are flushable and septic safe in well-maintained sewer and septic systems. Angel Soft Toilet Paper. Soft and strong. Simple.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: For a cloud-like experience, you don’t have to choose between a soft toilet paper and a strong one—Angel Soft Toilet Paper is a joyous balance of both. Our Mega Rolls are four times as big as our Regular Rolls, so you can change the roll less often! Angel Soft Toilet Paper breaks down easily after flushing and is safe for standard sewer and septic systems. Our sourcing practices are certified to the Sustainable Forestry Initiative (SFI) Fiber Sourcing Standard.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Delightful Blend of Comfort and Affordability!
reviews.reviewText: If there's one essential household item we can never have enough of, it's definitely toilet paper. I recently stumbled upon the perfect solution to this constant need – the Soft n' Cheap Bulk Toilet Paper! This product has exceeded my expectations in every way possible, and I couldn't be happier with my purchase.First and foremost, the softness of this toilet paper is simply outstanding. It provides a luxurious feel, making each bathroom trip a comforting and gentle experience. I was initially worried that buying in bulk might mean compromising on quality, but this toilet paper proved me wrong. The plush texture is comparable to high-end brands, if not better!What truly won me over is the unbeatable value for money. With the bulk packaging, I can forget about frequent trips to the store to stock up on toilet paper. The amount you get for the price is incredibly reasonable, and it has saved me both time and money in the long run. Now, I can confidently say goodbye to the days of running out of toilet paper unexpectedly.The packaging itself is quite convenient and easy to store. The rolls are individually wrapped, ensuring they remain hygienic until use. Moreover, the simple design blends seamlessly with any bathroom decor, which is a bonus!To sum it up, the Soft n' Cheap Bulk Toilet Paper is a dream come true for anyone seeking comfort, affordability, and convenience. It has certainly become a staple in my household, and I wholeheartedly recommend it to everyone in need of a reliable and budget-friendly toilet paper solution. You won't be disappointed!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best Deal Anywhere!!!
reviews.reviewText: This is some high quality stuff! Extremely soft! The rolls are super fat too! So thick that it might not even fit properly on your wall-mounted toilet paper roll holder it it's a small one. Definitely a lot of paper on each roll. Each roll truly is equal to 2 or more standard rolls offered by competitors. So, don't mistakenly think you've found a better deal just because you found another brand that offers more individual rolls for the same price or for a higher price. Also, keep in mind that some of those other sellers have a product that feels like you're wiping yourself with a brown paper bag! Not this though! It's 2-Ply, soft, and strong. Best deal around! Buy with confidence!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars TP was big during the pandemic
reviews.reviewText: When there is a shortage of TO and I had 3 boxes, my friends were happy. As a kid we had 7 kids and never enough toilet paper so I laugh that I have a stick in the garage. My kids wonder why I only let the roll get down to 20 percent and take it off. I chalk it up to childhood trauma, but each time I get a box of TP I am happy. Call me weird, but happy. The product is my favorite brand, it’s soft, it works and it arrives on time each month.
